""SELECT [t].[Id], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[CategoryId], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Content], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[DateCreated], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[DateModified], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([dtoProductCategory.Products].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Image], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Name], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[OriginalPrice], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Price], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[PromotionPrice], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[SeoAlias], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[SeoDescription], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[SeoKeywords], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[SeoPageTitle], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Status], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Tags], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[Unit], [dtoProductCategory.Products].[ViewCount]
FROM [Products] AS [dtoProductCategory.Products]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [dtoProductCategory0].[Id]
    FROM [ProductCategories] AS [dtoProductCategory0]

        WHERE (((CONVERT(date, [x16].[DateCreated]) >= @__start_Date_0) AND (DATEPART(month, [x16].[DateCreated]) >= @__start_Month_1)) AND (DATEPART(year, [x16].[DateCreated]) >= @__start_Year_2)) AND (((CONVERT(date, [x16].[DateCreated]) <= @__end_Date_3) AND (DATEPART(month, [x16].[DateCreated]) <= @__end_Month_4)) AND (DATEPART(year, [x16].[DateCreated]) <= @__end_Year_5))
        ORDER BY [x16].[DateCreated] DESC, [x16].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_6 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_7 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t42] ON [x.BillDetails6].[BillId] = [t42].[Id]
) AS [t43] ON [dtoBillDetail.Product.WholePrices0].[ProductId] = [t43].[Id1]

INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [dtoBillDetail.Size] ON [dtoProductCategory.Products.BillDetails].[SizeId] = [dtoBillDetail.Size].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [dtoBillDetail.Bill] ON [dtoProductCategory.Products.BillDetails].[BillId] = [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[Id]

    SELECT [t0].[Id], [dtoProductCategory.Products0].[Id] AS [Id0]

        SELECT 1
        FROM [Functions] AS [f]
